  Locus:
    Page: 377
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Prayer
---
Prayer is not a vain attempt to change God’s will： it is a filial desire to
learn God’s will and to share it. Prayer is not a substitute for work： it
is the secret spring and indispensable ally of all true work.
